ome.smuggler.core.types

Class ProcessedImport

  • java.lang.Object
    • ome.smuggler.core.types.ProcessedImport

  • public class ProcessedImport
extends java.lang.Object
    Same as a QueuedImport but only used after the import task has completed and needs to be garbage-collected.
